{"id": "art-916", "label": "Art. 916", "title": "Art. 916: Unele reguli specifice pentru finanţarea consorţiilor administrative", "slug": "art-916", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2015699273\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1515\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2015699273\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 91<sup>6</sup>:\nUnele reguli specifice pentru finan&#355;area consor&#355;iilor administrative </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1699605267\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1514\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1699605267\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Cuantumul contribu&#355;iei prev&#259;zute la art. 90\nalin. (1) se stabile&#351;te, pe baza unor criterii precum suprafa&#355;a sau\nnum&#259;rul utilizatorilor/beneficiarilor, de c&#259;tre adunarea\ngeneral&#259; a asocia&#355;iei, prin hot&#259;râre.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1351325857\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1513\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1351325857\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Autorit&#259;&#355;ile deliberative ale\nunit&#259;&#355;ilor administrativ-teritoriale membre în cadrul\nconsor&#355;iului administrativ pot stabili, în condi&#355;iile legii, taxe\nlocale speciale în vederea finan&#355;&#259;rii unor servicii publice locale\nfurnizate de consor&#355;iul administrativ.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_83976027\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1512\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_83976027\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Sumele încasate în bugetele locale, potrivit alin. (2),\nse aloc&#259; consor&#355;iilor administrative sub form&#259; de\ncontribu&#355;ii, în condi&#355;iile alin. (1).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_842551108\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1511\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_842551108\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Consor&#355;iile administrative pot percepe, în\ncondi&#355;iile legii, tarife în vederea finan&#355;&#259;rii serviciilor\npublice furnizate prin intermediul acestora.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}